snippet.title: Biden-Hur interview: Biden struggles to recall when son Beau died
snippet.description:
Axios obtained the audio of former President Biden's October 2023 interviews with special counsel Robert Hur.

In this clip, on the first day of interviews, former President Biden was questioned about where he kept documents. He had difficulty recalling that it was 2015 when his son Beau died. Biden also shared that President Obama discouraged him from running for president.

üì∏: Samuel Corum/Getty Images

Subscribe to keep up with the latest from the PGA Championship: https://bit.ly/PGAChampionshipYT‚ÄØ‚ÄØ 

Contested each May, the PGA Championship is the second major championship in golf‚Äôs annual rotation and perennially features the strongest field in the men's game based on the Official World Golf Rankings. Known for dramatic finishes and notable champions, the Wanamaker Trophy‚Äîwhich has been awarded to the winner since 1916‚Äîis inscribed with names such as Rory McIlroy, Tiger Woods, Phil Mickelson, Jack Nicklaus, and Gary Player.‚ÄØ
‚ÄØ

snippet.title: The Birth of BABY BLOBS (Pt. 1): Blob Universe #9
snippet.description:
The journey continues.....Let's keep going and see how many blob characters I can add to the collection today. It's going to be a lot of sculpting, customizing, and BLOBS. 

CHECK OUT THE AWFUL EVAN: https://moriahelizabethmerch.com/


___UPLOAD SCHEDULE___

Friday at 4:00pm ET

___________WELCOME TO MY CHANNEL__________

Hey! my name is Moriah (pronounced muh-rye-yuh) Elizabeth and this is my channel....obviously. I'm 30 and like doing creative activities (mostly painting on things), or really anything that gives me an excuse to use rainbows, sprinkles and my own cutesy characters in excess. I'm heavy into editing, so my video are chok-full of sound effects, filters and lil....moments, or as we like to call them "MEmes." I paint on squishies, thrift store finds, and various other items I find. I also love to draw, traditionally and digitally. I'm not the most skilled artist out here, but I like to focus on having fun with creativity and being able to laugh at my own mistakes. 

CURRENT SERIES:
Squishy Makeovers: Fixing and decorating used squishies sent from my viewers
Thrift Store Makeovers: Fixing and decorating stuff I find at thrift stores/yard sales
Bake With ME: Recreating squishies I've decorated in real life
Create This Book: Drawing in the prompt book that I wrote (available to purchase and follow along)
Squishy Unboxing: Opening used squishy packages sent from viewers
Drawings to Squishies: turning my flat drawings into squishies
Finishing Art Ideas: Choosing art ideas from my giant list and making them happen
Squishies I've Been Avoiding: Painting on the squishies I DON'T want to paint

Hey! my name is Moriah (pronounced muh-rye-yuh) Elizabeth and this is my channel....obviously. I'm 30 and like doing creative activities (mostly painting on things), or really anything that gives me an excuse to use rainbows, sprinkles and my own cutesy characters in excess. I'm heavy into editing, so my video are chok-full of sound effects, filters and lil....moments, or as we like to call them "MEmes." snippet.title: Superman | Official Trailer | DC
snippet.description:
Your choices, your actions, that‚Äôs what makes you who you are. #Superman - Only In Theaters and @Imax July 11

‚ÄúSuperman,‚Äù DC Studios‚Äô first feature film to hit the big screen, is set to soar into theaters worldwide this summer from Warner Bros. Pictures.  In his signature style, James Gunn takes on the original superhero in the newly imagined DC universe with a singular blend of epic action, humor and heart, delivering a Superman who‚Äôs driven by compassion and an inherent belief in the goodness of humankind. 

DC Studios heads Peter Safran and Gunn are producing the film, which Gunn directs from his own screenplay, based on characters from DC, Superman created by Jerry Siegel and Joe Shuster.

The film stars David Corenswet (‚ÄúTwisters,‚Äù ‚ÄúHollywood‚Äù) in the dual role of Superman/Clark Kent, Rachel Brosnahan (‚ÄúThe Marvelous Mrs. Maisel‚Äù) as Lois Lane and Nicholas Hoult (the ‚ÄúX-Men‚Äù movies, ‚ÄúJuror #2‚Äù) as Lex Luthor.  The film also stars Edi Gathegi (‚ÄúFor All Mankind‚Äù), Anthony Carrigan (‚ÄúBarry,‚Äù ‚ÄúGotham‚Äù), Nathan Fillion (the ‚ÄúGuardians of the Galaxy‚Äù films, ‚ÄúThe Suicide Squad‚Äù), Isabela Merced (‚ÄúAlien Romulus‚Äù), Skyler Gisondo (‚ÄúLicorice Pizza,‚Äù ‚ÄúBooksmart‚Äù), Sara Sampaio (‚ÄúAt Midnight‚Äù), Mar√≠a Gabriela de Far√≠a (‚ÄúThe Moodys‚Äù), Wendell Pierce (‚ÄúSelma,‚Äù ‚ÄúTom Clancy‚Äôs Jack Ryan‚Äù), Alan Tudyk (‚ÄúAndor‚Äù), Pruitt Taylor Vince (‚ÄúBird Box‚Äù) and Neva Howell (‚ÄúGreedy People‚Äù).

‚ÄúSuperman‚Äù is executive produced by Nikolas Korda, Chantal Nong Vo and Lars Winther.  Behind the camera, Gunn is joined by frequent collaborators, including director of photography Henry Braham, production designer Beth Mickle, costume designer Judianna Makovsky and composer John Murphy, along with composer David Fleming (‚ÄúThe Last of Us‚Äù) and editors William Hoy (‚ÄúThe Batman‚Äù) and Craig Alpert (‚ÄúDeadpool 2,‚Äù ‚ÄúBlue Beetle‚Äù).  

DC Studios Presents a Troll Court Entertainment/The Safran Company Production, A James Gunn Film, ‚ÄúSuperman,‚Äù which will be in theaters and IMAX¬Æ nationwide on July 11, 2025, and internationally beginning 9 July 2025, distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures.

en.title: Superman | Official Trailer | DC
en.description:
Your choices, your actions, that‚Äôs what makes you who you are. #Superman - Only In Theaters and @Imax July 11

‚ÄúSuperman,‚Äù DC Studios‚Äô first feature film to hit the big screen, is set to soar into theaters worldwide this summer from Warner Bros. Pictures.  In his signature style, James Gunn takes on the original superhero in the newly imagined DC universe with a singular blend of epic action, humor and heart, delivering a Superman who‚Äôs driven by compassion and an inherent belief in the goodness of humankind. 

DC Studios heads Peter Safran and Gunn are producing the film, which Gunn directs from his own screenplay, based on characters from DC, Superman created by Jerry Siegel and Joe Shuster.

The film stars David Corenswet (‚ÄúTwisters,‚Äù ‚ÄúHollywood‚Äù) in the dual role of Superman/Clark Kent, Rachel Brosnahan (‚ÄúThe Marvelous Mrs. Maisel‚Äù) as Lois Lane and Nicholas Hoult (the ‚ÄúX-Men‚Äù movies, ‚ÄúJuror #2‚Äù) as Lex Luthor.  The film also stars Edi Gathegi (‚ÄúFor All Mankind‚Äù), Anthony Carrigan (‚ÄúBarry,‚Äù ‚ÄúGotham‚Äù), Nathan Fillion (the ‚ÄúGuardians of the Galaxy‚Äù films, ‚ÄúThe Suicide Squad‚Äù), Isabela Merced (‚ÄúAlien Romulus‚Äù), Skyler Gisondo (‚ÄúLicorice Pizza,‚Äù ‚ÄúBooksmart‚Äù), Sara Sampaio (‚ÄúAt Midnight‚Äù), Mar√≠a Gabriela de Far√≠a (‚ÄúThe Moodys‚Äù), Wendell Pierce (‚ÄúSelma,‚Äù ‚ÄúTom Clancy‚Äôs Jack Ryan‚Äù), Alan Tudyk (‚ÄúAndor‚Äù), Pruitt Taylor Vince (‚ÄúBird Box‚Äù) and Neva Howell (‚ÄúGreedy People‚Äù).

‚ÄúSuperman‚Äù is executive produced by Nikolas Korda, Chantal Nong Vo and Lars Winther.  Behind the camera, Gunn is joined by frequent collaborators, including director of photography Henry Braham, production designer Beth Mickle, costume designer Judianna Makovsky and composer John Murphy, along with composer David Fleming (‚ÄúThe Last of Us‚Äù) and editors William Hoy (‚ÄúThe Batman‚Äù) and Craig Alpert (‚ÄúDeadpool 2,‚Äù ‚ÄúBlue Beetle‚Äù).  

DC Studios Presents a Troll Court Entertainment/The Safran Company Production, A James Gunn Film, ‚ÄúSuperman,‚Äù which will be in theaters and IMAX¬Æ nationwide on July 11, 2025, and internationally beginning 9 July 2025, distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures.

snippet.title: Kelly Clarkson & Blake Shelton Try To Keep It Professional During Hilarious Interview
snippet.description:
Blake Shelton dishes on his first album in four years, "For Recreation Use Only," including how working with Post Malone lit a fire under him to make another record, and which song is his favorite. Blake also reflects on his top 5 live performances from his career, including being mistaken for Terri Clark at the 2002 Fan Fair in Nashville, getting inducted into the Grand Ole Opry, and singing karaoke with George Strait.

snippet.description:

------

Article - https://www.axios.com/2025/05/01/mcdonalds-restaurants-fast-food-recession-starbucks

-----

Edited By: Svibe Multimedia Studio

Music Courtesy of: Epidemic Sound

üì© Business Inquiries ‚û°Ô∏è sponsors@worksmedia.group

Sign up for our newsletter https://compoundeddaily.com üëà

All materials in these videos are for educational purposes only and fall within the guidelines of fair use. No copyright infringement intended. This video does not provide investment or financial advice of any kind.

#business #finance 
-----

Fast food has never been GOOD food, but it was a quick, easy, reliable and cheap way to get a meal that appealed to people who were time poor‚Ä¶ or just well‚Ä¶ you know‚Ä¶ actually poor‚Ä¶
Mass layoffs, increasing economic uncertainty, deferred student loan payments kicking in and spiking levels of consumer debt SHOULD be the perfect opportunity for these cheap offerings to bring in customers who don‚Äôt have much money to spare, but still want to eat. 
For a long time companies like McDonalds, Dominos, KFC, Taco Bell and Wendy‚Äôs were considered ‚Äúrecession proof‚Äù because even in the most dire of circumstances people still need to eat, and the companies typically offered the best exchange rate of dollars to calories in the market. 
But that‚Äôs changed. 
In a business move that can only be described as‚Ä¶ confusing‚Ä¶ These brands have responded to cost conscious, busy and desperate consumers by becoming more expensive, slower and less reliable‚Ä¶ 
Unsurprisingly sales across the industry have plummeted at a time when they SHOULD be outperforming. 
It would almost be comical if they weren‚Äôt collectively some of the largest employers in the country.
However the McRessession has been caused by more than some management missteps, it‚Äôs a clear sign of some much bigger problems in the wider economy.

snippet.title: Americana (2025) Official Trailer ‚Äì Sydney Sweeney, Paul Walter Hauser, Halsey
snippet.description:
Americana ‚Äì in theaters August 22, 2025. Starring Sydney Sweeney, Paul Walter Hauser, Halsey, Simon Rex, with Eric Dane, and Zahn McClarnon

Subscribe to the LIONSGATE: YouTube Channel for the latest movie trailers, clips, and more: https://bit.ly/2Z6nfym

https://www.lionsgate.com/movies/
https://www.facebook.com/lionsgate
https://twitter.com/lionsgate
https://www.instagram.com/lionsgate/
https://www.tiktok.com/@lionsgate

A gallery of dynamic characters clash over the possession of a rare Native American artifact in this wildly entertaining modern-day western. After the artifact falls onto the black market, a shy waitress with big dreams (Sydney Sweeney) teams up with a lovelorn military veteran (Paul Walter Hauser) to gain possession of it, putting them in the crosshairs of a ruthless criminal (Eric Dane) working on behalf of a Western antiquities dealer (Simon Rex). Bloodshed ensues when others join the battle, including the leader of an indigenous group (Zahn McClarnon) and a desperate woman fleeing her mysterious past (Halsey).

snippet.title: Gary Sinise Speaks Out About His Son's Death & Why He Left Hollywood | PEOPLE
snippet.description:
Gary Sinise shares his story of stepping away from Hollywood to care for his family and grieve the unimaginable loss of his son, Mac. The actor opens up for the first time about Mac‚Äôs battle with chordoma, a rare, slow-growing spinal cancer, and the strength his son showed throughout his illness: ‚ÄúThe way he dealt with it was just pure grace and courage.‚Äù He reveals the moment they discovered Mac‚Äôs tumor on a CT scan, after months of unexplained pain: ‚ÄúIt looks like a monster grabbing my son‚Äôs spine.‚Äù Gary reflects on a harrowing period that began with his father‚Äôs stroke, followed by his wife‚Äôs stage 3 breast cancer treatment and his son‚Äôs shocking diagnosis ‚Äî and the decision he made to pause acting to care for them. Mac passed away on January 5, 2024. Gary‚Äôs wife is now cancer-free.

He has continued his work with the Gary Sinise Foundation, which supports veterans, first responders, and their families. Gary recently produced ‚ÄòBrothers After War‚Äô, a documentary about wounded heroes returning from combat, and is helping release Mac‚Äôs final music. The songs are now available, with proceeds going to the Foundation in honor of Mac‚Äôs wishes. Gary also shares the joy he finds in being a grandfather, a role that brings light amid the pain. He will return to Washington, D.C. to host the Foundation‚Äôs annual Memorial Day concert. Gary Sinise offers an intimate look at life, loss, and legacy in the wake of profound personal tragedy.

snippet.title: A Minecraft Movie | Chicken Jockey | Movie Clip | Warner Bros. Entertainment
snippet.description:
Chicken Jockey!! Watch the movie clip from A Minecraft Movie where Garrett (Jason Momoa) must fight a baby zombie mounted on a chicken in order to save Steve (Jack Black). Welcome to the world of Minecraft, look for the movie on digital.

Four misfits‚ÄîGarrett ‚ÄúThe Garbage Man‚Äù Garrison (Momoa), Henry (Hansen), Natalie (Myers) and Dawn (Brooks)‚Äîfind themselves struggling with ordinary problems when they are suddenly pulled through a mysterious portal into the Overworld: a bizarre, cubic wonderland that thrives on imagination. To get back home, they‚Äôll have to master this world (and protect it from evil things like Piglins and Zombies, too) while embarking on a magical quest with an unexpected, expert crafter, Steve (Black). Together, their adventure will challenge all five to be bold and to reconnect with the qualities that make each of them uniquely creative‚Ä¶the very skills they need to thrive back in the real world.

snippet.title: Brooklyn Gets Surgery * FOR REAL * This Time
snippet.description:
I bet you‚Äôre wondering ‚ÄúBrooklyn gets surgery *FOR REAL* ?‚Äù....Last year I was diagnosed with a skenes gland cyst and was scheduled for surgery right after I came home from Everest. Unfortunately, when they went to remove the cyst, it had ruptured and they were unable to remove it. Well a year later,  my cyst came back in my third trimester, so it was time to go in for another surgery to have it removed, for real this time!! 

For anyone going through something like this, my heart goes out to you. The medical world is a big and confusing place and I hope nothing but the best for you!!

snippet.title: Diddy Trial: Cassie's Testimony Breakdown With CBS News' Jericka Duncan
snippet.description: CBS News' Jericka Duncan breaks down Cassie Ventura's testimony against her ex, Sean 'Diddy' Combs, in his sex trafficking and racketeering trial on Tuesday, May 13. Diddy maintains his innocence against all charges, currently being explored in a New York City court. Jericka recounts Cassie's explanation of 'freak offs,' the supposed sex-fueled parties thrown by Diddy, and abuse she allegedly experienced while dating Diddy. Jericka also speculates on other famous faces who may take the stand in the coming days.

snippet.title: Nobody 2 | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Nobody ruins his vacation. #Nobody2 hits theaters August 15.

---
Sometimes the most dangerous place for a dad is a family vacation.

Bob Odenkirk returns as suburban husband, father and workaholic assassin Hutch
Mansell in the new chapter to Nobody, the hit 2021 bare-knuckle action-thriller that
opened at number one at the U.S. box office.

Four years after he inadvertently took on the Russian mob, Hutch remains $30 million in debt to the criminal organization and is working it off with an unending string of hits on international thugs.

Much as he likes the slam-bang action of his ‚Äújob,‚Äù Hutch and his wife Becca
(International Emmy nominee Connie Nielsen) find themselves overworked and drifting apart. Acid Betty, Aja, Alyssa Hunter, Bosco, Cynthia Lee Fontaine, Daya Betty, DeJa Skye, Denali, Ginger Minj, Irene the Alien, Jorgeous, Kerri Colby, Lydia B Kollins, Mistress Isabelle Brooks, Nicole Paige Brooks, Olivia Lux, Phoenix, and Tina Burner are spilling tea, throwing shade, and taking a wild walk down memory lane as they react to every jaw-dropping, gag-worthy, and meme-spawning moment in Drag Race history. 

From Ongina‚Äôs emotional reveal in Season 1 to Nymphia Wind‚Äôs surprise win in Season 16 (and yes, even Lydia Butthole Kollins‚Äô roast redemption in Season 17), no queen, wig, or runway is safe. Watch your faves laugh, cry, and kiki their way through the iconic highs, the cringe-y lows, and the drama we still talk about today. This is the ultimate Ru-view ‚Äî by the queens, for the queens.

snippet.title: Helldivers 2 - Weapon Customization
snippet.description:
Gear up, Helldivers‚Äîyour arsenal just got personal! 
With the new Weapon Customization system, you can now tailor your favorite weapons to match your combat style and preferences once you‚Äôve progressed and unlocked different attachments. Whether it's tweaking sights for precision, changing color patterns, adjusting magazines for ammo capacity, muzzles to optimize weapon performance characteristics or adjusting underbarrels for the handling you want, you're in command of how your weaponry performs on the battlefield. 
Tinker in the menu, customize your specific weapon configs and switch between them during the mission loadout sequence.
It's time to fight for Super Earth with weapons that are truly yours!

Video Patch Notes: https://youtu.be/Cca-KKScFKc?si=fcdp7SuUY6YTJRXc

snippet.title: $10 Million Barnfind: Jay Leno Reveals the Rarest Mercedes Gullwing Ever Discovered
snippet.description:
This is what buried treasure looks like in 2025. üí∞ Jay Leno uncovers one of the most extraordinary automotive discoveries in recent history ‚Äî a 1956 Mercedes-Benz Alloy Gullwing, one of just 29 ever made, and the only unrestored survivor. Hidden away in a Los Angeles storage garage for nearly 60 years, this ultra-rare, all-aluminum Gullwing was once forgotten ‚Äî until now.

Jay walks us through the incredible backstory, the preservation details, and why this hand-built piece of Mercedes racing history sold for nearly $10 million. This isn‚Äôt just a car ‚Äî it‚Äôs a time capsule.

Don‚Äôt miss this once-in-a-lifetime look inside one of the most important barn finds in automotive history.

snippet.title: Jeff Teague REACTS to Pacers ENDING Cavs, Thunder take lead on Nuggets, Jayson Tatum torn achilles
snippet.description:
On the Wednesday, May 14 episode of 520 in the Morning, Jeff Teague, DJ Wells, and B Hen react to Tyrese Haliburton and the Indiana Pacers advancing to the eastern conference finals for the second year in a row after finishing off Donovan Mitchell and the Cleveland Cavaliers in 5 games. Jeff reacts to Shai Gilgeous-Alexander and the Oklahoma City Thunder taking a 3-2 lead on Nikola Jokic and the Denver Nuggets, as well as Jayson Tatum‚Äôs confirmed torn achilles which will keep him out for the entirety of next season.

The Ariel Atom 4R (¬£70,000 starting) and the Caterham Seven 620S (¬£58,490 starting) both subscribe to similar philosophies, but both have a different execution. Lightweight power may be the goal, but the Atom employs a massively turbocharged Civic Type R engine and lots of driving mode customization. Whereas the Caterham pushes a supercharged Ford Duratec engine combined with a raw 5-speed manual option. snippet.title: F1 The Movie | Main Trailer
snippet.description:
Lights out - and away they go! #F1TheMovie only in theaters June 27. #F1Movie #F1

From Apple Original Films and the filmmakers from Top Gun: Maverick comes the high-octane, action-packed feature film F1¬Æ The Movie, starring Brad Pitt and directed by Joseph Kosinski.  The film is produced by Jerry Bruckheimer, Kosinski, seven-time FORMULA 1¬Æ world champion Lewis Hamilton, Pitt, Dede Gardner, Jeremy Kleiner and Chad Oman.

Dubbed ‚Äúthe greatest that never was,‚Äù Sonny Hayes (Brad Pitt) was FORMULA 1‚Äôs most promising phenom of the 1990s until an accident on the track nearly ended his career.  Thirty years later, he‚Äôs a nomadic racer-for-hire when he‚Äôs approached by his former teammate Ruben Cervantes (Javier Bardem), owner of a struggling FORMULA 1 team that is on the verge of collapse.  Ruben convinces Sonny to come back to FORMULA 1 for one last shot at saving the team and being the best in the world.  He‚Äôll drive alongside Joshua Pearce (Damson Idris), the team's hotshot rookie intent on setting his own pace.  But as the engines roar, Sonny‚Äôs past catches up with him and he finds that in FORMULA 1, your teammate is your fiercest competition‚Äîand the road to redemption is not something you can travel alone.

F1¬Æ The Movie also stars Damson Idris, Kerry Condon, Tobias Menzies, Kim Bodnia, and Javier Bardem, and was shot during actual Grand Prix weekends as the team competed against the titans of the sport.

Kosinski directs from a screenplay by Ehren Kruger, story by Kosinski & Kruger.  The film is executive produced by Daniel Lupi.  Collaborating with Kosinski behind the scenes are his creative team, including director of photography Claudio Miranda, production designers Mark Tildesley and Ben Munro, editor Stephen Mirrione, costume designer Julian Day, casting director Lucy Bevan and composer Hans Zimmer.

Apple Original Films and Warner Bros. Pictures Present A Monolith Pictures / Jerry Bruckheimer / Plan B Entertainment / Dawn Apollo Films Production, A Joseph Kosinski Film, F1¬Æ The Movie, distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures, in theaters and IMAX¬Æ nationwide on June 27, 2025 and internationally beginning 25 June 2025.

snippet.title: 1 killed, 32 hospitalized after Mother's Day morning crash involving tour bus on 60 Freeway
snippet.description:
A person died and 32 people were hospitalized, including two in critical condition, after a tour bus crash on the 60 Freeway in Hacienda Heights early Sunday morning.
KTLA 5's Erin Myers reports. (May 11, 2025)

snippet.title: This Undefeated 32 Inch "Monster" Burrito Challenge in Arkansas Weighs 8lbs!!
snippet.description:
Taking on the undefeated 32 inch "Monster" 8lb Burrito Challenge at Las Fresas Mexican Grill in Van Buren, Arkansas! Hungry diners have just 45 minutes to finish a burrito loaded with steak, chicken, chorizo, shrimp, french fries, rice, refried beans, guacamole, sour cream, and veggies. Along the way you must finish all of the sauces including a huge bowl of queso, and a bowl of chili Colorado and salsa verde. Winners earn their meal for free, a groovy t-shirt, and a spot up on Las Fresas' Wall of Fame! 
***
RP Strength Code: KILOS
RP Diet App Link: https://rp.app/diet/code/KILOS
RP Hypertrophy App Link: https://rp.app/hypertrophy/code/KILOS
***
INSTAGRAM: https://www.instagram.com/katinaeatskilos/
WEBSITE: https://www.katinaeatskilos.com
***
About Me:
I'm a 5'2 former women's physique bodybuilder on a mission to sample delicious foods from around the world! I tackle restaurant challenges, sample new food menus, and explore the unique eats in various cities. To balance out the calorie intake of weekly food challenges, I continue to pursue my love of fitness through bodybuilding, running, and spinning. 

FAQ:
**How do you not get fat?** 
Please check out my "Daily Diet" Playlist Here: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLcjzJq-PMUB7ovX5rYVzA1GITfvCtq3P3

**Why do you shake so much?**
I have a genetic condition known as "non-essential tremors". That in combination with nerves, being hungry with lowered blood sugar, and a deep and profound love affair with caffeine, makes for a rather jittery start to a challenge.

**Are you and Randy married?** 
No, not yet! We got engaged on December 1, 2024 though and are excited for the future!
